<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: #ffffff;
            color: #333;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #0066cc;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            background: #ffffff;
        }

        .content p {
            margin: 0 0 16px;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: normal;
            color: #333;
        }

        .button-container {
            text-align: left;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #0066cc;
            color: white !important;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .link-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            word-break: break-all;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        .link-box p {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .link-box a {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 13px;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .notice {
            background: #fffbea;
            border-left: 4px solid #f4b400;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .notice p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #856404;
        }

        .notice strong {
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #888;
        }

        .divider {
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">Hello <%= name %>,</p>

            <p>We received a request to reset your password for your <strong>Email Verification App</strong> account.
            </p>

            <p>To reset your password, click the button below:</p>

            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="<%= resetUrl %>" class="button">Reset My Password</a>
            </div>

            <p style="color: #888; font-size: 14px;">This button will take you to a secure page where you can create a
                new password.</p>

            <div class="link-box">
                <p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
                <a href="<%= resetUrl %>">
                    <%= resetUrl %>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="notice">
                <p><strong>Security Notice:</strong> If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this
                    email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666;">This password reset link will expire in <strong>1 hour</strong> for
                security reasons.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">
                If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team.
            </p>

            <p style="margin-top: 25px; color: #666;">
                Best regards,<br>
                <strong style="color: #333;">Email Verification App Team</strong>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong style="color: #333;">Email Verification App</strong></p>
            <p>&copy; 2026 All rights reserved.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; margin-top: 15px; color: #999;">
                This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>